data.description: Well kept home on large cul-de-sac lot tucked away in the wooded area of subdivision, all located in popular Mandeville school district, and just a short drive to Causeway Bridge.  Very nice and clean inside, but the outdoors are most impressive, and green views can be enjoyed from your den, sunroom, master bedroom, or the rear patio.  Bedrooms are spacious & two have walk-in closets.  All windows have been replaced, along with kitchen appliances and HW heater.  Extra storage along rear of detached carport.  Refrigerator, washer & dryer included!
data.whatILove: The privacy, many trees, and large lot.  Also, very close to Causeway bridge for easy commutes to NOLA.  Mandeville schools have earned many blue ribbons, check out www.stpsb.org for details.
